      "span_text": "Critically, the property exhibited by our model to learn identical weights for the same letters at different locations appears not to be limited to backpropagation or to visual words, as it has recently been mirrored on a non-linguistic training base and with the Trace rule, a hebbian learning rule with a temporal window [CITATION_1] ."
